Sony Suspends Plan to Raise Its Stake in Sharp's LCD Panel Venture

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-04-27T06:18:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/sony-suspends-plan-to-raise-stake-in-sharp-panel-venture.html
Sony Corp. (6758)  suspended a plan to
raise its stake in a liquid-crystal-display panel venture with
Sharp Corp.  Sony had earlier reached an agreement to raise its stake in
Sharp Display Products Corp. to 34 percent, from 7.04 percent.
The two electronics makers will continue talks on the investment
until the end of March 2012, according to a joint statement to
the Tokyo Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
